title: macOS High Sierra 10.13.6 +Adobe Photoshop+Microsoft Office
description: macOS High Sierra 10.13.6 (17G65)July 9, 2018 Adobe Photoshop CC 2018.1.5 v19.1.5 Microsoft Office Standard 2016 v16.12 (64-bit) macOS High Sierra is Apple's next operating system for Mac computers. The new version of the OS did not bring updates to the appearance of the platform and was limited to improvements in the level of functionality. High Sierra is the successor to the previous version of macOS Sierra and has several notable improvements such as the new APFS file system and support for various modern technologies such as virtual reality and machine learning. http://cracutillus.ddns.net/1516775734
